result.title: Marking clarification on 750B
result.content:
According to the marking available @ http://codeforces.com/contest/750/submission/23444822, my solution fails on subtest 2 where I return YES on expected NO.

However, on running the test on my local system the solution returns the expected NO. Executing it on repl.it @ https://repl.it/Ey7G/1 returns NO. Local system version is 2.7.11, repl.it version is 2.7.10.

Any clarification would be welcome
